Statement of unknown bystander regarding an encounter with The Archivist

Thanks to this week's Patrons: Ashley Temple, Emilie Mont, micah (birdkaiju), Eric Carr, Michaela, Carineybean, Luke Davies, Elizabeth Krueger, Cody Jarrett, Lydia Counsell, Sharra Rosichan, TheZenScientist, Rexy, Adaar David Durand, Anne Poelman, Neil Kelly, szgrey, Ian Moran, Sean McMahon, Xander, Wizard of the Citadel Under the Hidden Rivers, etc.


If you'd like to join them be sure to visit www.patreon.com/rustyquill

- Martin Blackwood - Alexander Newall

- Alice 'Daisy' Tonner,- Fay Roberts
